\begin{document}
}{}$^{\mathrm{6}}$\end{document} MCMC iterations following a discarded burn-in of 10,000 iterations. We checked for convergence between the two runs and combined the MCMC samples to produce estimates of the posterior probabilities of various delimitation models. For all datasets, we placed diffuse gamma priors \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
